            <ab>Athenodoros to Poseidonios and Demetria, greeting. If you and the children are healthy, it is as I want. I myself am healthy as well. If Heliodoros has not yet sent you � (here the papyrus breaks off.) (On the verso) To Poseidonios and Demetria � from Athenodoros.</ab>
